Tati, YES, you are right. The public shouldn’t do what they do to make a hype out of somebody’s pain, but you need to understand that those creepy asses want to destroy your energy to refil theirs. What I want to tell you, is that I have learned not to discuss my health so deeply. People are not going to understand, UNTIL they have such problems.
Leave them alone with themselves.
Take care of yourself.

Girl. Put that energy into your wellbeing, mirrage, company. Your fans will understand.
There is no reason to explain yourself, unless you are feeling uncomfortable with it. Keep that in mind.
Peace!

But when I start to use the brush any loose hairs fall out. And over time if i dont maintain my brush correctly, i let it stay wet too long, i dry it upright so water stays near the barrel. I'll lose more fibres.
